{
  "meta": {
    "source": "documented_official_linear_mcp_launch_set",
    "endpoint": "https://mcp.linear.app/mcp",
    "method": "tools/list",
    "protocol": "JSON-RPC 2.0 streamable HTTP",
    "captureDate": "2026-07-21",
    "launchToolCount": 20,
    "notes": [
      "Frozen from Linear's publicly documented MCP tool surface (issues/projects/comments/teams/users/statuses/labels/cycles).",
      "Documents tools (list/get/create/update_document) are out of launch scope — cold/unsupported.",
